data.description: Assumable 3.125% Mortgage! Welcome to country living on 2.2 acres just outside of town. This spacious Pennfield ranch offers 3 beds, 2 1/2 baths, an updated kitchen, SS appliances, cozy fireplace in the living room, laundry and a large dining area all on the main level with over 1700 sq ft. There are a gorgeous views of wildlife, woods and the neighbor's pond from virtually every window. The basement is neat and clean and offers fresh paint, a huge rec room with endless possibilities, a gorgeous fireplace, tiled zero entry full bath, non-conforming 4th bedroom and tons of storage. The 32x24 pole barn w/separate electric meter and large 2 car attached garage are great for full sized pickup trucks. Generator hookup. Sellers converted to gas so furnace & AC are 2 yrs old. Call today
